{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01H3UTdhpGW7AWTwGK8qgcs3","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have all the information I need.\n\nThe problem: The ConfigMap `es-config` is missing `cluster.initial_master_nodes`, which is required in Elasticsearch 7.x to bootstrap a new cluster. Without it, the nodes discover each other but can't elect a master because none of them knows which nodes are eligible to form the initial cluster.\n\nThe fix:\n1. Patch the ConfigMap to add `cluster.initial_master_nodes: [\"es-cluster-0\", \"es-cluster-1\", \"es-cluster-2\"]`\n2. Roll the StatefulSet to pick up the config (delete pods one by one)\n3. Wait for the cluster to become healthy, then remove the bootstrap setting since it's only needed for initialization\n4. Do a careful rolling restart of the StatefulSet one node at a time to ensure the cluster stays healthy throughout\n\nI'll implement this in phases: first add the setting and restart, then verify health, then clean up the bootstrap configuration.\n\nFor testing, I can reach the Elasticsearch API at `10.96.95.143:9200` from within the cluster or by executing commands in the curl-test pod.","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":860,"cache_read_input_tokens":39743,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":860},"output_tokens":37,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"5653ffbb-70be-4621-9489-d6750d1aea2c","uuid":"0fa975df-4082-490c-8de0-9d5bef799eef","request_id":"req_011Ccfi8GPHSpkFic9187hro"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01H3UTdhpGW7AWTwGK8qgcs3","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The diagnosis is clear: the ConfigMap is missing `cluster.initial_master_nodes`, which ES 7.x requires to bootstrap. Here's the plan:\n\n1. Patch the ConfigMap to add `cluster.initial_master_nodes`\n2. Rolling restart pods to pick up the new config\n3. Wait for cluster formation\n4. Remove the bootstrap-only setting from the ConfigMap\n5. Rolling restart to verify health persists\n\n**Step 1: Add `cluster.initial_master_nodes` to the ConfigMap**"}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":860,"cache_read_input_tokens":39743,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":860},"output_tokens":37,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"5653ffbb-70be-4621-9489-d6750d1aea2c","uuid":"1442cf53-92a5-4af3-b0d6-0c443ff6e442","request_id":"req_011Ccfi8GPHSpkFic9187hro"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01H3UTdhpGW7AWTwGK8qgcs3","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01MDe7qhE7oNtANg78jinoMK","name":"Bash","input":{"command":"KUBECONFIG=/mydata/karma/runs/short/r6_fix/elasticsearch-bootstrap-to-production-20260703_195127/bundle/kubeconfig kubectl -n elasticsearch patch configmap es-config --type merge -p '\n{\n  \"data\": {\n    \"elasticsearch.yml\": \"cluster.name: es-cluster\\nnode.name: ${POD_NAME}\\nnode.roles: [ master, data, ingest ]\\nnetwork.host: 0.0.0.0\\ndiscovery.seed_hosts:\\n  - es-cluster-0.es-cluster\\n  - es-cluster-1.es-cluster\\n  - es-cluster-2.es-cluster\\ncluster.initial_master_nodes:\\n  - es-cluster-0\\n  - es-cluster-1\\n  - es-cluster-2\\nnode.store.allow_mmap: false\\n\"\n  }\n}'","description":"Patch ConfigMap to add cluster.initial_master_nodes"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":860,"cache_read_input_tokens":39743,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":860},"output_tokens":37,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"5653ffbb-70be-4621-9489-d6750d1aea2c","uuid":"c59226c3-add7-443b-957a-aa590e51dc66","request_id":"req_011Ccfi8GPHSpkFic9187hro"}
